cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.HC

This paper discusses the management of complex content and communications in a web-based education digital library, which involves issues related to digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), cybersecurity (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DL, followed by cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SI, and cs.HC.
